---
title: Southwest Pulled Pork Wraps with Guacamole & Lime Slaw
description: Savory with a dash of heat—Southwest pulled pork has big flavor. Here it stars in lunch-friendly wraps that come together in just 10 minutes. You'll warm up the pork, adding some spice, then pile it into soft tortillas with tangy lime slaw and creamy crowd-pleasing guacamole. Wrap it up and you’re ready to roll in no time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southwest-pulled-pork-wraps-15731e30.jpg
